{"title":"San Util Designs Roly Poly Handlebar Bag","link":"https://theradavist.com/san-util-designs-roly-poly-handlebar-bag/","date":1710511920000,"content":"<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1362\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/SanUtilRolltopHandlebarBag-24.jpg?fit=1200,1362&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/SanUtilRolltopHandlebarBag-24.jpg?w=2048&amp;quality=75 2048w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/SanUtilRolltopHandlebarBag-24.jpg?resize=1200,798&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/SanUtilRolltopHandlebarBag-24.jpg?resize=2000,1330&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/SanUtilRolltopHandlebarBag-24.jpg?resize=768,511&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/SanUtilRolltopHandlebarBag-24.jpg?resize=1536,1022&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p>Colorado had a killer ski season this year and even in between powder days, developing an ultralight backpack system, Adam from San Util still developed a completely all-new product; the <a href=\"https://sanutildesign.com/collections/bikepacking-adventure/products/roly-poly-handlebar-bag\" target=\"_blank\">Roly Poly Handlebar Bag</a> ($145). Let’s check it out.<span></span></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1362\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/SanUtilRolltopHandlebarBag-15.jpg?fit=1200,1362&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/SanUtilRolltopHandlebarBag-15.jpg?w=2048&amp;quality=75 2048w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/SanUtilRolltopHandlebarBag-15.jpg?resize=1200,798&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/SanUtilRolltopHandlebarBag-15.jpg?resize=2000,1330&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/SanUtilRolltopHandlebarBag-15.jpg?resize=768,511&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/SanUtilRolltopHandlebarBag-15.jpg?resize=1536,1022&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1362\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/SanUtilRolltopHandlebarBag-18.jpg?fit=1200,1362&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/SanUtilRolltopHandlebarBag-18.jpg?w=2048&amp;quality=75 2048w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/SanUtilRolltopHandlebarBag-18.jpg?resize=1200,798&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/SanUtilRolltopHandlebarBag-18.jpg?resize=2000,1330&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/SanUtilRolltopHandlebarBag-18.jpg?resize=768,511&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/SanUtilRolltopHandlebarBag-18.jpg?resize=1536,1022&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p>The Roly Poly is San Util’s medium-sized handlebar bag that is roughly 3L and overstuffable to about 5L. Features include side stretch pockets that are covered by the roll top “lid”, a zipper front pocket, front daisy chains and adjustable loops underneath, as well as 2 small drop pockets inside to separate out all the goodies.</p>\n<p>When paired with other bags, this bag is perfect for a long day of gravel grinding or a multi-day bike tour, or even a bikepacking race like the CTR.</p>\n<p><em>San Util’s Colorado Trail setup is a set of Mini Panniers, a Small Frame Bag, 2 Stem Bags, and this Handlebar Bag.</em></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1362\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/SanUtilRolltopHandlebarBag-26.jpg?fit=1200,1362&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/SanUtilRolltopHandlebarBag-26.jpg?w=2048&amp;quality=75 2048w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/SanUtilRolltopHandlebarBag-26.jpg?resize=1200,798&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/SanUtilRolltopHandlebarBag-26.jpg?resize=2000,1330&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/SanUtilRolltopHandlebarBag-26.jpg?resize=768,511&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/SanUtilRolltopHandlebarBag-26.jpg?resize=1536,1022&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1362\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/SanUtilRolltopHandlebarBag-28.jpg?fit=1200,1362&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/SanUtilRolltopHandlebarBag-28.jpg?w=2048&amp;quality=75 2048w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/SanUtilRolltopHandlebarBag-28.jpg?resize=1200,798&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/SanUtilRolltopHandlebarBag-28.jpg?resize=2000,1330&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/SanUtilRolltopHandlebarBag-28.jpg?resize=768,511&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/SanUtilRolltopHandlebarBag-28.jpg?resize=1536,1022&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2048\" height=\"1362\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/SanUtilRolltopHandlebarBag-11.jpg?fit=1200,1362&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/SanUtilRolltopHandlebarBag-11.jpg?w=2048&amp;quality=75 2048w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/SanUtilRolltopHandlebarBag-11.jpg?resize=1200,798&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/SanUtilRolltopHandlebarBag-11.jpg?resize=2000,1330&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/SanUtilRolltopHandlebarBag-11.jpg?resize=768,511&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/SanUtilRolltopHandlebarBag-11.jpg?resize=1536,1022&amp;quality=75 1536w\" /></p>\n<p><strong>KEY FEATURES:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Side Pockets</li>\n<li>Zipper Front Pocket</li>\n<li>Overstuffable</li>\n<li>Lashing Points on Exterior</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>PRODUCT DIMENSIONS:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>w10″ x h7″- h12″ x d4.5″</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>PRODUCT WEIGHT:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>EPX200 – 268g</li>\n<li>1000D Cordura – 310g</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>PRODUCT VOLUME</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Roughly 2.5L – 5L</li>\n</ul>\n<p>MADE IN USA – Winter Park Colorado</p>\n<p>See more at <a href=\"https://sanutildesign.com/collections/bikepacking-adventure/products/roly-poly-handlebar-bag\" target=\"_blank\">San Util Designs</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/san-util-designs-roly-poly-handlebar-bag/\">San Util Designs Roly Poly Handlebar Bag</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"a1b3fa89d435ffdf787de9fdc33616877f0b9d609de51ce1b0fda93b7b399e1b","category":"Cycling"}